'''恰伦河'''（{{lang-ru|Чарын}}, {{lang-kk|Шарын}}, ''Sharyn''）是[[哈萨克斯坦|哈萨克斯坦]][[阿拉木图州|阿拉木图州]]的一条河流，全长{{convert|427|km|mi}}，流域面积{{convert|7720|km2}}。其流经{{link-en|恰伦国家公园|Charyn National Park}}，注入[[伊犁河|伊犁河]]，并形成了{{link-en|恰伦大峡谷|Charyn Canyon}}。<ref>[http://bse.sci-lib.com/article121531.html Чарын] {{Wayback|url=http://bse.sci-lib.com/article121531.html |date=20190719044701 }}，[[苏联大百科全书|苏联大百科全书]]</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=About park |url=http://charyn.kz/eng/about-the-park/ |website=Charyn State National Natural Park |date=2016 |access-date=2021-02-03 |archive-date=2021-02-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210207182641/http://charyn.kz/eng/about-the-park/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite book |last1=Brummell |first1=Paul |title=Kazakhstan |date=2011 |publisher=Bradt Travel Guides |isbn=9781841623696 |page=170 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=CH3PY_LSOlAC |language=en |access-date=2021-02-03 |archive-date=2020-06-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200614133353/https://books.google.com/books?id=CH3PY_LSOlAC |dead-url=no }}</ref>{{link-en|玛依纳水电站|Moinak Hydro Power Plant}}设于恰伦河上。<ref name="AstTim">{{cite news |last1=Kalymov |first1=Asset |title=SPAIID Project Providing Power to Southern Kazakhstan - The Astana Times |url=https://astanatimes.com/2013/12/spaiid-project-providing-power-southern-kazakhstan/ |work=The Astana Times |date=3 December 2013 |accessdate=2021-02-03 |archive-date=2018-06-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180612141347/https://astanatimes.com/2013/12/spaiid-project-providing-power-southern-kazakhstan/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

恰伦河有许多发源自[[泰尔斯凯山脉|泰尔斯凯山脉]]和{{link-en|昆格山脉|Küngöy Ala-Too Range}}北坡的支流汇入。其在扎拉纳什和托鲁艾格尔地区切割出一条[[峡谷|峡谷]]。峡谷在扎拉纳什被称为“阿克托盖”，在哈萨克语中意为“白溪”。

